result.execSummary:
The defendant Gabriel Mondragon-Gutierrez was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Gabriel Mondragon-Gutierrez is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Gabriel Mondragon-Gutierrez was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
